Reginald Denny (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reginald_Denny_(actor) 0 Reginald Denny (born Reginald Leigh Dugmore, 20 November 1891 – 16 June 1967) was an English stage, film and television actor as well as an aviator and UAV pioneer. He was once an amateur boxing champion of Great Britain.
